data.description: Price improvement! Beautiful move-in ready 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in the desirable Pulewa at Mehana community. Enjoy this fantastic layout where you are greeted by an open floorplan that leads to a spacious covered lanai with bonus storage. Unit includes split AC in every room with a large walk-in closet in the primary bedroom. In-unit stacked washer dryer. Community amenities include large pool, gym, playground, walking paths, and more! Two parking stalls (one covered, one uncovered) and guest stalls throughout the complex. Convenient to shops, restaurants, eateries, parks and Ho‘okele Elementary School. Book your showing today!
